==Route and stages==

The [[List of highest points reached in the Tour de France|highest point of elevation in the race]] was {{convert|2115|m|ft|abbr=on}} at the summit of the [[Col du Tourmalet]] mountain pass on stage 14.{{sfn|Augendre|2016|p=188}}<ref>{{cite news|title=88th Tour de France – The Major Climbs|url=http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/results/2001/tour01/stages/stages.shtml|access-date=23 December 2019|website=[[Cyclingnews.com]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803163139/http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/results/2001/tour01/stages/stages.shtml|archive-date=3 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>

